Det er ikke en af mine favoritter.

961
01:20:51.434 --> 01:20:55.935
Det bliver okay.

962
01:20:56.859 --> 01:20:59.985
Okay?

963
01:21:00.153 --> 01:21:03.029
Okay.

964
